{"name":"IDR23 App. E: Rime of the Frostmaiden","folder":"v7gab0UjDkz2EUl6","sort":2300000,"flags":{"srd5e":{"source":"IDRotF","entryIds":["7a7","7a8"]}},"_id":"fMfM6lNafqoikgBB","pages":[{"name":"IDR23 App. E: Rime of the Frostmaiden","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<div class=\"w-100 h-100 overflow-x-hidden\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"2233\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Appendix E: Rime of the Frostmaiden</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></span> <div class=\"rd__b-special rd__b-inset \"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--2-inset rd__h--2-inset-no-name\"><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-special-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></span><p>We bow to She who wears the crown; Let the world shiver with dread. Clad in winter's whitest gown, Her snow enshrouds the dead.</p><p>Her fury sheds but frozen tears as gray clouds issue forth. Her wind across the wasteland shears, bringing blizzards from the north.</p><p>Ice-kissed flowers caught mid-bloom, beauty kept in all its grace. Summer's gone to its silent tomb, stilling in Her cold embrace.</p><p>All the world in winter's white, sheathed in sleet and ice. Set upon never-ending night, She conjures paradise.</p><p>Behold Her everlasting rime, see how it covers all; Weep not for those She traps in time behind Her glacial wall.</p><p>Sovereign of summers lost, general of winter's war; Long live the queen of cold and frost. May She reign forevermore.</p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div></div><p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/adventure/IDRotF/262-08-021.rime-of-the-frostmaiden.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/img/adventure/IDRotF/262-08-021.rime-of-the-frostmaiden.jpg\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div></div>"},"_id":"sKK297aFOH41Myg5","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"PP5XOkXk6hNdYKV4":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}
{"name":"IDR22 App. D: Magic","folder":"v7gab0UjDkz2EUl6","sort":2200000,"flags":{"srd5e":{"source":"IDRotF","entryIds":["786","787","795","798"]}},"_id":"j49PswuO0sqybvo0","pages":[{"name":"IDR22 App. D: Magic","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<div class=\"w-100 h-100 overflow-x-hidden\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"2229\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Appendix D: Magic</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></span> <p>This appendix describes the new magic items, spellbooks, and spells found in this adventure.</p><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"2230\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Magic Items</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></span> <p>New magic items found in this adventure are presented below in alphabetical order.</p><ul class=\"rd__list columns-3\"><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[ycjafDXNgMnj95IF]{Abracadabrus}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[Xd25hIUCXoquVkyS]{Cauldron of Plenty}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[XqrNNkANOvhZj5wy]{Hook of Fisher's Delight}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[C2ucUjYFpZKUm0Rp]{Lantern of Tracking}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[hzQsdKlAnpeQ8aFT]{Professor Orb}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[BESKrl18nVWGtoe1]{Professor Skant}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[uUPrY1xDiabbohSR]{Psi Crystal}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[W5IMjTzvgVTL6jxt]{Scroll of Tarrasque Summoning}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[k33DmK3Xt4sRXlIC]{Scroll of the Comet}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[XpAa5MZYNu12upbD]{Thermal Cube}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[LpiVj9Lcu3RMtOEq]{Ythryn Mythallar}</li></ul></div><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"2231\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Books</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></span> <p>Two books are described in this section. Characters can find @Item[j8tDVg3eloi05U12]{The Codicil of White} in Auril's abode (see <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/adventure.html#IDRotF,15\">chapter 5</a>) and @Item[i4zue9spb8tozTA5]{The Incantations of Iriolarthas} in the Netherese necropolis hidden under the Reghed Glacier (see <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/adventure.html#IDRotF,17\">chapter 7</a>).</p></div><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"2232\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Wizard Spells</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></span> <p>Characters who obtain @Item[j8tDVg3eloi05U12]{The Codicil of White} from Auril's abode or @Item[i4zue9spb8tozTA5]{The Incantations of Iriolarthas} in Ythryn can discover one or more of the following wizard spells.</p><ul class=\"rd__list columns-3\"><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[WQJbyIrqu6H7eDlb]{Blade of Disaster}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[0gOvScSRQZ5l24za]{Create Magen}</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@Item[qfumQ5UBnVB2ogPB]{Frost Fingers}</li></ul></div></div></div>"},"_id":"kCIFIW9XhjQQiCPA","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"PP5XOkXk6hNdYKV4":3},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}}
